created an independent regulatory agency and licensed a second
national operator.
</P>
<P>
There has been a steady progress in the process of
privatization. As at the end of February this year, a total of
80 public enterprises had been privatized. Steps have also been
taken to privatize 13 other enterprises.
</P>
<P>
The privatization of the Uganda Posts and Telecommunications
Corporation is the focus of the 1997/1998 program.  
</P>
