<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, December 5 (Xinhua) -- The gold price in Hong Kong
remained unchanged from the previous close at 2,696 HK dollars a
tael on Saturday, according to Po Sang Bank, one of the major gold
dealers in Hong Kong.
</P>
