<HEADLINE> Sweden Leads Italy 2-0 in Davis Cup Final </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ROME, December 4 (Xinhua) -- Magnus Gustafsson defeated Davide
Sanguinetti in straight sets to give Sweden a commanding 2-0 lead
over Italy at the end of the opening day of the Davis Cup final
in Milan on Friday.
</P>
<P>
