a 6-1, 6-4, 6-0 victory before more than ten thousand spectators.
</P>
<P>
In the first singles, Sweden's Magnus Norman beat Italian
Andrea Gaudenzi 6-7 (9-11), 7-6 (7-0), 4-6, 6-3. The Italian
retired hurt in the fifth set with score at 6-6.
</P>
<P>
Sweden's doubles duo of Jonas Bjorkman and Niklas Kulti will
take on Italy's Diego Nargiso and Sanguinetti on Saturday.
